{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after two weeks, or two and 1/2 weeks, we were told, in a few days, you will leave here, and we will take you on a trip.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will reassign you for some work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you can take with you not any more on wagons, just what you can carry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Before we-- yeah, and then we-- everybody started to [? solve ?] some kind of bags-- handbags, little suitcases, knapsacks, whatever and to pack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know, from the little things we brought from home, what to take along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But what happened during those few weeks, every day the SS used to come in and pick a group of young men for some kind of work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took them behind the city and-- digging something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what work it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day, my brother was picked, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was about 18 years old at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we heard that they are taking us away the next day, and he didn't show up-- this is one of the things I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father was a tall man, six feet tall, very healthy, always a smile on his face, but not-- I didn't see a smile on his face since the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when they advanced, and he didn't come home, he was going up and down, up and down, waiting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was afraid they will take us away, and he won't be with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe it would have been for the best, but we didn't know it at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, it was almost dark, he came home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he ran to my brother, and he hugged and kissed him, and he started to cry.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
